{"tid":2432314,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"疫苗接種 | 患心臟病老婦少理副作用照打針：我都幾十歲人唔怕啦","createTime":"2021-03-04T08:40:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-04T19:36:57.000Z","uid":130626,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"b8c12985f905efff07f2b0070c24ab4466147168","tid":2432314,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T08:40:41.000Z","msg":"79歲的關太說：「啲人講到嚇哂人咁，我都幾十歲人唔怕啦！」但其實她患有心臟病，早前進行通波仔手術，至今仍要長期服藥，今早未服藥便趕到來。接種中心的醫生得悉此情況，勸她服藥後再前來接種，結果她回家服藥休息一會後再到來打針。<br />\n<br />\n關太一知半解地說：「支針係我哋應該要打嘅，而且約咗4月2號再打第二針。」她指接種後沒有特別，針口位「有少少㷫㷫哋」。<br />\n<br />\n另一位67歲的張先生指接種程序不繁複，說：「唔驚呀！點解要好驚呢？啲專家話無事、話唔關事。」張先生更向記者展示疫苗接種記錄表，「因為呢隻科興最早嘛，早打早着」，但未考慮再接種疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n李小姐在碼頭工作，任職貨運業，屬於優先接種疫苗的群組。她表示不擔心疫苗，揚言身體狀況極佳；而且醫生更多次詢問其病歷，令她更安心。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/fs8uR47bnUjOmdXLzQEqSKiuZAY=/1599x899/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HS243CPSINGMPN537WPYWUCLSE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Ffs8uR47bnUjOmdXLzQEqSKiuZAY%3D%2F1599x899%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHS243CPSINGMPN537WPYWUCLSE.jpg&h=990abf74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n79歲的關太曾進行過通波仔手術，醫生勸指若未服藥，不能夠接種疫苗。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/4_Ex2j-MC4uy0Ro5_rdlm4ppS_o=/1600x900/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3OLAOSES4RCN3LOOQLSLEBPXJI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F4_Ex2j-MC4uy0Ro5_rdlm4ppS_o%3D%2F1600x900%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3OLAOSES4RCN3LOOQLSLEBPXJI.jpg&h=a19e7b73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n67歲的關先生說：「唔驚呀！點解要好驚呢？啲專家話無事 話唔關事。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/KHuCs0wul4o3VWVj7HpGOdaGndM=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/I3UV2BOVLVGZXHYW4NPFBQEERE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FKHuCs0wul4o3VWVj7HpGOdaGndM%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FI3UV2BOVLVGZXHYW4NPFBQEERE.jpg&h=2d217a19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n李小姐表示合乎資格優先接種疫苗。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210304/VDJV3P7QTBG3ZKKBQCWV5VVU54/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210304%2FVDJV3P7QTBG3ZKKBQCWV5VVU54%2F&d=Xhragic3nybqeCAZBODyv%2F1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=e011c147\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210304%2FVDJV3P7QTBG3ZKKBQCWV5VVU54%2F&h=9cf72b4d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210304/VDJV3P7QTBG3ZKKBQCWV5VVU54/</a>"},{"pid":"28dd3e5e1fe01b764a5d9935d64d61778d9327f1","tid":2432314,"uid":54800,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T08:43:18.000Z","msg":"早打早著~~<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27364184826957dc53cf3cdc5b1146385ca03ec1","tid":2432314,"uid":7369,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T08:43:30.000Z","msg":"咁副作用又唔係個個都會有嘅, 不過打科興得52%都打就白痴咗小小囉!"},{"pid":"0d7ba5564fc08405ba3439bcbdf7613312ea9140","tid":2432314,"uid":182485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T08:44:33.000Z","msg":"想呃錢？無甘易"},{"pid":"e6fb353903a9998c106593e49fe436adf79b8813","tid":2432314,"uid":51583,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T08:44:39.000Z","msg":"你唔怕但你死左政府又怕呢"},{"pid":"a9a8c51892c14ecf8c39dfd5e8141c9fde3274c3","tid":2432314,"uid":89696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T08:46:40.000Z","msg":"好呀!講得好!支持!<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee84558e2